title: G.I. Joe - Die Abrechnung
description: The G.I. Joe team is framed for crimes against the country by Zartan, disguised as the President, and Cobra Commander has all the world leaders under his influence, with their advanced warheads headed towards innocent populaces around the world. Outnumbered and outgunned, the surviving team members form a plan with their original leader, General Joseph Colton, to rescue the President and face off Cobra Commander, his accomplices and the world leaders. Written by Anonymous
castList: [Dwayne Johnson, Jonathan Pryce, Byung-hun Lee, Elodie Yung, Ray Stevenson, D.J. Cotrona, Adrianne Palicki, Channing Tatum, Ray Park, Luke Bracey, Walton Goggins, Arnold Vosloo, Joseph Mazzello, Nick Erickson, RZA]
characterList: [Roadblock, President, Storm Shadow, Jinx, Firefly, Flint, Jaye, Duke, Snake Eyes, Cobra Commander, Warden Nigel James, Zartan, Mouse (as Joe Mazzello), President Picture Double, Blind Master]
